snippet.title: Cause of Death - Volume 1 - The Maskmaker (2010)
snippet.description:
Volume 1, the very first volume, of Cause of Death: Can You Catch The Killer? Released by EA Mobile in 2010, with episodes released from 2010-2014, before the game was delisted from the App Store in 2014. iOS game available on iPad, iPhone, iPod, etc..

List of included episodes with timecodes below.

All episodes credited to Amy Chen. Videos automatically stitched together with Moviepy.

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLXFROtmHmfIXcFs3N_7mKIUMXhwDQQugs

0:00 - V1C1: Washed Up

16:50 - V1C2: The Masks We Wear

33:52 - V1C3: Bad Medicine

49:49 - V1C4: Buried Secrets

1:03:27 - V1C5: Unmasked

1:26:32 - V1C6: The Devil's Island
